## Deploying the Frontend

### Option A — Zip upload
```bash
cd dist && zip -r ../deploy.zip . && cd ..
curl -s -X POST "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/sites/$SUPABEIN_SITE_ID/deploys" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN" \
  -F "zipfile=@./deploy.zip" \
  -F "label=v1.0.0"
```

### Option B — File by file (CI/CD friendly)
```bash
# 1. Open a deploy
DID=$(curl -sX POST "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/sites/$SUPABEIN_SITE_ID/deploys/open" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"label":"v1.0.0"}' | python3 -c "import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin)['id'])")

# 2. Upload each file
find dist -type f | while read f; do
  REL="${f#dist/}"
  curl -sX PUT "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/sites/$SUPABEIN_SITE_ID/deploys/$DID/files?path=$REL" \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN" \
    --data-binary "@$f"
done

# 3. Go live
curl -sX POST "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/sites/$SUPABEIN_SITE_ID/deploys/$DID/finalize" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN"
```

The live site is then at: `$SUPABEIN_URL/sites/s$SUPABEIN_SITE_ID/current/`

### Rollback
```bash
curl -sX POST "$SUPABEIN_URL/api/v1/projects/$PROJECT_ID/sites/$SUPABEIN_SITE_ID/deploys/$DEPLOY_ID/rollback" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $SUPABEIN_TOKEN"
```

